Entries.default: "The company offices are always busy. I hope that means business is good."
"Seems you're always going up or down stairs in Neketaka."
"Queen's Berth is pleasant enough, but reeks of the docks."
"They say the view from Serpent's Crown is beautiful."
"Sacred Stair is the city's divine heart. Visit to pay thanks to the gods."
"Ought to let the Bardatto boy fight his own battles."
"That Valera boy could have won by himself, you know."
"Shame about Orso. Always thought he was misunderstood."
"They say Larro Bardatto bled out in a fight. He was always trouble."
"Wonder what happens when the adra has all dried up."
